'''Eugene Addor''' was a Swiss [[Shooting sport|sports shooter]]. He competed at the [[1920 Summer Olympics]] winning a bronze medal in the [[Shooting at the 1920 Summer Olympics – Men's 300 and 600 metre team military rifle, prone|team military rifle]] event.<ref name="sportsref">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ad/eugene-addor-1.html |title=Eugen Addor |accessdate=19 December 2014 |work=Sports Reference |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002094703/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ad/eugene-addor-1.html |archivedate=2 October 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>

